column2: SELECT FLOOR(sppParams.l/#)*#, AVG(s.z*#e5/cos(radians(sppParams.b))) v_doppler,         STDEV(s.z*#e5/cos(radians(sppParams.b)))/SQRT(COUNT(*)) err  FROM SpecObj s  INNER JOIN sppParams ON s.specObjID = sppParams.specobjiD  WHERE s.z < # and s.z># and sppParams.feha > # and sppParams.feha < # and sppParams.b<#  GROUP BY FLOOR(sppParams.l/#)*#  ORDER BY #
